  <h1>💥 DAN’S BUCKS – THE EASTER APOCALYPSE EDITION 💥</h1>
  <p><strong>Operation: Farewell to Dan’s Dignity</strong> is officially locked in for Easter 2026. That’s right—while the rest of the country eats chocolate eggs and pretends to be wholesome, we’ll be embracing our inner goblins.</p>
  <p>This is not a family-friendly event. There will be paint. There will be partying. There will be decisions we swear felt right at the time.</p>

  <h2>🎯 Mission Breakdown:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Phase One – Paintball:</strong> Gear up, maggots. We’re taking to the battlefield to settle scores, ruin friendships, and find out who panics when a twelve-year-old with a paintball gun charges them screaming.</li>
    <li><strong>Phase Two – Airbnb Chaos HQ:</strong> Our post-battle sanctuary. A den of beers, BBQ, and questionable life choices. Will someone fall asleep in the garden holding a half-eaten kebab? Probably.</li>
    <li><strong>Phase Three – After-dark Entertainment (Toppy’s Galore):</strong> Premium morale support. Respectful. Tasteful. Just enough to make your phone's front camera wish it was never activated.</li>
    <li><strong>Phase Four – Post-Toppy Adventure:</strong> Australia's night scene. Will someone get kicked out of a pub? Definitely. Will they deserve it? Absolutely.</li>
  </ul>

